
00:00:01,635 --> 00:00:04,204
Narrator:
Tonight on "Shark Tank"...
Come on! Who wants to make
a lot of dough?!

00:00:04,204 --> 00:00:05,339
Whoa!

00:00:05,339 --> 00:00:06,874
